internal path (existing). === SPECTRAL (SOUND-NAN-v2) === UNIT test_finite_f64_construction: FiniteF64::new(f64::NAN) == None, FiniteF64::new(f64::INFINITY) == None, FiniteF64::new(1.0) == Some. UNIT test_finite_f64_arithmetic: addition, subtraction, multiplication of finites → finite. UNIT test_finite_f64_checked_div: checked_div by zero → None. checked_div by nonzero → Some. UNIT test_finite_f64_ord: FiniteF64 total ordering consistent with f64 partial ordering for finite values. PROPTEST test_spectral_metrics_always_finite: Random N×N (N=1..10) adjacency matrix, all entries finite. All spectral metrics return Some(finite) or None, never panic. UNIT test_degenerate_empty_graph: 0 nodes → all None. UNIT test_degenerate_single_node: PageRank = 1.0, spectral gap = None. UNIT test_degenerate_fully_disconnected: N isolated nodes → Fiedler = 0. UNIT test_degenerate_fully_connected: all metrics finite. UNIT test_eigensolver_convergence_flag: well-conditioned matrix → converged=true. Ill-conditioned → converged=false with approximate values. === RESOLUTION (SOUND-LATTICE) === UNIT test_lattice_fallback_records_actual_mode: Configure Lattice for attr, create conflict, verify actual_mode == LWW. UNIT test_resolution_receipt_includes_fallback_reason: non-empty reason string. === E2E SCRIPT scripts/e2e_foundation_soundness.sh === (1) cargo test --lib -- store::tests::test_incremental_batch_duality (exit 0). (2) cargo test --lib -- store::tests::test_live_view (3 tests, exit 0). (3) cargo test --lib -- guidance::tests::mt_session (2 tests, exit 0). (4) cargo test --lib -- guidance::tests::spec_language_turns (2 tests, exit 0). (5) cargo test --lib -- query::graph::tests::test_degenerate (4 tests, exit 0). (6) cargo test --lib -- resolution::tests::test_lattice_fallback (exit 0). (7) Fresh braid init on tmpdir, braid status → output contains no 'NaN'. (8) braid observe with em-dash → exit 0 (no panic). (9) 100 observations in loop, braid status after each → F(S) always finite. 